<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7935210d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1976—<ref href="/us/pl/94/273">Pub. L. 94–273</ref> substituted “September” for “June”.</p>
